QuestData.Title: Reclaiming Ahn'Kahet
QuestData.Description: Prince Taldaram and his army of Scourge use the same wards we once used to hide our empire to keep themselves safe from the native denizens of the icy depths.$B$BDeactivate the wards and slaughter the Scourge guarding them. My forces will help the natives slaughter the rest.
QuestData.PortraitTurnInText: I must ask one more favor of you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Seer Ixit in Ahn'Kahet wants you to kill 3 Eyes of Taldaram, a Bonegrinder, and Prince Taldaram.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent.$B$B<You heard a series of clicking sounds.>$B$BNow to vanquish our other foe.
